[試題] 103-2 李克強 中等數值方法 期中考
作者 r3399r
看板 Ntu-exam
時間
                
                    2015-07-09 23:50:16
                
            
課程名稱︰ 中等數值方法
課程性質︰ 選修
課程教師︰ 李克強
開課學院： 工學院
開課系所︰ 化工系
考試日期（年月日）︰ 2015.04.20
考試時限（分鐘）： 120

試題 :

Intermediate Numerical methods Midterm

1. Find the solution of the following nonlinear algebraic equation with
   Newton-Raphson iteration method: (25%)

    3
   x = sinx







2. Find the Lagrange interpolating polynomial passing through the following
   data points: (25%)

     x  │  0 │ 1.0│ 2.0│ 3.0
  ───┼──┼──┼──┼───
   y(x) │ 2.7│ 1.2│-1.3│ 0.8

   What is the value of y(1.5) according to the interpolating polynomial?

3. Redo problem (2) by using Newton's forward difference interpolating
   polynomial and evaluate y(1.5) accordingly. (25%)

4. Redo problem (3) by using Newton's backward difference interpolating
   polynomial. (25%)


